                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>). I was not told where to find the pri<lb></lb>soner—I met him accidentally—I went to a Mr. Burt's to ask him to come for some work, and there I saw the prisoner sitting on the board, and I recognised him as the man; he held his head down.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner received a good character.</hi>
